      "image": "https://assets.deadbydaylight.com/S51_Eleven_b635ee0ebb.png",
      "sourceTitle": "Eleven",
      "description": "Jane \"Eleven\" Hopper (née Ives) is one of 52 Survivors currently featured in Dead by Daylight.\nShe was introduced as a Survivor of CHAPTER 38: Stranger Things Chapter 2, a Chapter DLC released on 27 January 2026. \nShe originates from the 2016 Sci-Fi-Horror Web Television series Stranger Things, specifically from season 5.",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-18T14:17:03Z",
      "descriptionPt": "Criada em cativeiro e estudada por suas habilidades psíquicas, a garota solitária chamada Onze nunca teve uma conexão significativa. Ela encontrou um novo propósito após sua fuga: proteger seus amigos do perigo, custe o que custar.",
