      "image": "https://deadbydaylight.wiki.gg/images/thumb/New_Store_Shape.png/420px-New_Store_Shape.png?2d776e",
      "sourceTitle": "Michael Myers",
      "description": "Michael Myers or \"The Shape\" is one of 42 Killers featured in Dead by Daylight.\nHe was introduced as the Killer of CHAPTER 2: The HALLOWEEN® Chapter, a Chapter DLC originally released on 25th of October 2016 which was retired on 19th of January 2026.\nHe remains a fully playable and supported Character in Dead by Daylight for all Players who purchased him before his Chapter left the Game.\nHe originates from the 1978 Horror Movie franchise with the same name, Halloween.",
