      "description": "Elliot Spencer or \"The Cenobite\", also known as \"Pinhead\", is one of 42 Killers currently featured in Dead by Daylight. \nHe was introduced as the Killer of CHAPTER 21: Hellraiser™, a Chapter DLC released on 7 September 2021, which was delisted from platform stores on 4 March 2025 and 13 March 2025 for the Nintendo eShop.\nHe remains a playable Character for all Players who purchased him prior to 4 April 2025.\nHe originates from the 1987 Horror Movie franchise, Hellraiser.",
