      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Imai",
      "description": "Adriana Imai or \"The Skull Merchant\" is one of 42 Killers currently featured in Dead by Daylight.\nShe was introduced as the Killer of CHAPTER 27: Tools of Torment, a Chapter DLC released on 7 March 2023 and retired on 14 May 2024.\nShe is still available in the In-Game Store and as part of the Endless Hunt Pack Chapter Pack DLC.",
