      "description": "Charles Lee Ray or \"The Good Guy\", also known as \"Chucky\", is one of 42 Killers currently featured in Dead by Daylight.\nHe was introduced as the Killer of CHAPTER 30: Chucky, a Chapter DLC released on 28 November 2023.\nHe originates from the 1990 Supernatural Slasher franchise Child's Play, specifically from Child's Play 2.",
