      "sourceTitle": "Vecna",
      "description": "For the Stranger Things character also known as \"Vecna\", click here.\n\nVecna or \"The Lich\" is one of 42 Killers currently featured in Dead by Daylight.\nHe was introduced as the Killer of CHAPTER 32: Dungeons & Dragons, a Chapter DLC released on 3 June 2024.\nHe originates from the 1974 Board game Dungeons & Dragons, specifically its fifth edition from 2014.",
