      "sourceTitle": "Hex: Overture of Doom",
      "description": "Hex: Overture of Doom is a Unique Perk belonging to The Krasue.Prestige The Krasue to Prestige 1, 2, 3 respectively to unlock Tier I, Tier II, Tier III of Hex: Overture of Doom for all other Characters.",
