      "sourceTitle": "EMP",
      "description": "Limited Item\nAn electromagnetic pulse device that is printed by Supply Cases when facing The Singularity.\nThe Auras of Supply Cases are visible when within 28 metres:\n*Takes 100 Charges to be printed.\n**Passive printing charges at a rate of +1 c/s, but is limited to 97 Charges, requiring the final 3 Charges to be actively printed by a Survivor.\n**Active printing charges at a rate of +4 c/s while a Survivor interacts with the Supply Case.\n*Takes 2.5 seconds to charge.\n*Incurs a -10 % Hindered Status Effect while charging and holding.\n*Has an Area of Effect of 10 metres.\n*Removes Temporal Slipstream from anyone within its Area of Effect upon detonation.\n**The Auras of other Slipstreamed Survivors are revealed to you in yellow when within the Area of Effect.\n*Disables all Biopods within the Area of Effect for 45 seconds upon detonation and grants immunity to Temporal Slipstream for 1 second.\nLimited Items are consumed on use.\nThey cannot be brought back to the Campfire after a Trial and are removed by The Entity upon exiting the Trial.",
