      "sourceTitle": "Glowing Fungus",
      "description": "Limited Item\nSpawns in the environment when facing The Krasue:\n*When spawned, takes 5 seconds to grow and become interactable.\n*Can be picked up by Survivors.\n*Reveals its Aura to all Survivors afflicted with Leeched within 128 metres.\nPress the Use Item button to eat the mushroom:\n*Takes 3 seconds to complete.\n*Limits movement to walking.\n*Reduces the Walking speed to 70.8 % of its default value.\n**This effect lingers for 0.5 seconds.\nAfter eating a Glowing Fungus, Survivors benefit from the following effect:\n*Depletes the Leeched Meter at a rate of -5 %/s.\n**This effect ends after being hit.\nDropping a Glowing Fungus on the ground causes it to decay within 5 seconds unless a Survivor is within 2.5 metres of its location.\nLimited Items are consumed on use.\nThey cannot be brought back to the Campfire after a Trial and are removed by The Entity upon exiting the Trial.",
      "image": "https://deadbydaylight.wiki.gg/wiki/Special:Redirect/file/iconItems_glowingFungus.png",
      "updatedAt": "2025-09-07T13:25:02Z",
