      "description": "Limited Vecna Item\nPress the Use Item button to attune to the Hand of Vecna:\n*Triggers Killer Instinct for 5 seconds.\n*Grants The Lich the ability to kill you by his own hand, once you have accumulated 2 Hook Stages and are in the Dying State.\nWhile healthy, you benefit from the following effect:\n*The Aura of whichever Locker is nearest to your current location is revealed to you and highlighted in yellow.\nPerform a Rushed action to enter the highlighted Locker to activate a special ability:\n*Instantly teleports you to a different Locker at least 10 metres away.\n*Triggers a Loud Noise Notification at that location.\n*Removes 1 Health State.\n*Causes you to suffer from the Broken</span ></span ></span ></span ></span ></span > Status Effect for 30 seconds.\nThe Hand of Vecna can retrieved from a Treasure Chests when rolling a 20 upon opening it.\nLimited Vecna Items are depleted on use but kept on your person.\nThey cannot be brought back to the Campfire after a Trial and are removed by The Entity upon exiting the Trial.",
