      "category": "Limited",
      "charges": "",
      "sourceTitle": "Candelabra",
      "description": "Limited Item\nIn the darkest of castles, any light is a precious commodity.\nAll Survivors start the Trial with a Candelabra held in hand.\n*Additional Candelabras may be found in Chests located in the environment.\n*The Auras of all Candelabras placed in the environment are revealed to all Survivors in white at all times.\n*Pushes back the Fog as a passive effect when held.\nPress and hold the Use Item button while holding the Candelabra to benefit from the following effects:\n*90 Charges.\n*The Aura of the nearest incomplete Generator is revealed to you.\n*The Survivor Activity HUD is displayed to you, but without any visible Progression.\nPlace the Candelabra on top of a Generator to benefit from the following effects:\n*The Aura of that Generator is revealed to all Survivors within 32 metres.\n*Completing that Generator causes it to suppress the Killer's ability to read the Auras of all remaining incomplete Generators for 15 seconds or until the Candelabra is removed from it by any means.\n*Can be destroyed by the Killer when placed on Generators.\nThe Candelabra is only available for use in the Lights Out - Castlevania Modifier Event.\nLimited Items are consumed on use.\nThey cannot be brought back to the Campfire after a Trial and are removed by The Entity upon exiting the Trial.",
      "image": "https://deadbydaylight.wiki.gg/wiki/Special:Redirect/file/iconItems_fireflyLantern.png",
