      "sourceTitle": "Void Crystal",
      "description": "Limited Item\nCan be retrieved from the Void Well in exchange for 70 Void Energy and has 1 Charge.\nPress the Use Item button to shatter the Void Crystal at your feet and release a thick Fog Cloud:\n*Expands to its maximum size of 4 metres over 1 second.\n*Lasts for 8 seconds.\n*Obscures visibility and sounds for all Players within its Area of Effect.\n*Grants special benefits to its user:\n**Grants them full invisibility while inside the Fog Cloud and their own Aura is revealed to them, highlighted in white.\n**Suppresses the creation of their Scratch Marks while within 2–6 metres of the centre of the Fog Cloud.\nPress the Use Item button while standing next to an incomplete Generator to lay the Void Crystal atop of it:\n*Automatically repairs the Generator at a rate of 0.8 %/s for a maximum of 30 seconds.\n**This disables the ability to manually repair that Generator while active.\n**The Killer can stop the auto-repair prematurely by damaging that Generator, which destroys the Void Crystal.\nThe Void Crystal is only available during Halloween Events.\nLimited Items are consumed on use.\nThey cannot be brought back to the Campfire after a Trial and are removed by The Entity upon exiting the Trial.",
