      "description": "Limited Item\nThe handle is slick, and blood wells between your fingers as you tighten your grip.\nThe Blood Can is found when interacting with the Blood Pump and required to carry the blood needed to repair Blood Generators:\n*Holds a maximum of 40 Litres of blood:\n**Loses -0.5 L/s when left on the ground.\n**Loses -0.7 L/s while running.\n**Loses -20 Litres when toppled over.\n*Running produces Pools of Blood.\n*Emits distinct noises while carried, which vary depending on your Movement speed and the number of Litres of blood being carried.\nWhile filling the Blood Can at a Blood Pump, you benefit from the following effect:\n*The Aura of the nearest Blood Generator is revealed to you.\n**This effect lingers for 10 seconds.\nThe Blood Can vanishes from the Trial when empty and is only available during Spring Events.\nLimited Items are consumed on use.\nThey cannot be brought back to the Campfire after a Trial and are removed by The Entity upon exiting the Trial.",
